8 December 2008President Kgalema Motlanthe will announce his decision on the Ginwala Enquiry report into Mr Vusi Pikoli s fitness or otherwise to hold office.Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Monday, 8 December 2008 (Today) Time: 11:00 Venue: Union Buildings, Pretoria, Room 153 [bring press cards]There will be video link to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.RSVP Matshepo Seedat (Pretoria) Cell: 083 228 5041Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Enquiries Thabo Masebe Cell: 082 410 8087Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)